Ingeniero Carlos Casamiquela,

7
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:20,640
el señor representante
en la Argentina

8
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,840
del Banco Interamericano
de desarrollo,

9
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,320
don Hugo Florez Timoran,

10
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:27,000
